  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd - \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A mother with her two children jumped into the Embilipitiya Vavi - the mother also lost her life",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police say a mother with her two children jumped into the Chandrika Basin in Embilipitiya, killing her aunt and her 5-year-old child, while her 11-year-old son survived.",
        "Police said that Surangika Madhumali, a 32-year-old mother from Suriyawewa area with her two children had entered the well from the mouth of the Chandrika well.",
        "After the mother jumped into the wavi with her two children, her 11-year-old son, Sam Tushmanda, somehow swam to the shore and screamed for help.",
        "Residents and police lifeguards immediately jumped into the Chandrika pond and rescued the mother and 5-year-old son.",
        "However, as the condition of both of them was still critical, they were immediately taken to Embilipitiya Hospital, where the 5-year-old died at 1.45 pm. While the mother was still receiving treatment in the intensive care unit, she also died in the evening.",
        "In this situation, 2 thousand rupees cash and a phone have been seized from the mother, and the police have started investigations regarding the cause of the incident."
      ],
